  stimulus_text = 'The sentence "When I first moved to a new city, I felt like a fish out of water, but I quickly adapted to my new surroundings."  is grammatically correct. However, the sentence "When I first moved to a new city, I felt like a fish out of water, but I quickly adapted to my new surroundings, and I was very happy." is grammatically incorrect. Which change to the second sentence would make it grammatically correct?',
